PEMEX Procurement International |   Supplier Directory
















































 

 















Supplier DirectoryYou are here: Home / Suppliers / Supplier Directory
The Approved Suppliers’ Directory represents a unique source of information for PEMEX buyers that has been carefully researched and evaluated. They can be confident that all suppliers found in the Directory are a viable source for the product or service that they are seeking – both for upstream and downstream operations. Buyers can locate suppliers by their name, brand name, and type of product offered.


Before suppliers can be registered, they must go through a stringent set of screening criteria to meet the minimum legal, administrative, technical and financial requirements. Our intention is to establish solid commercial relationships with suppliers, preferably dealing with the most reliable of suppliers capable of providing the best options in terms of QUALITY, PRICE, DELIVERY TIMES and SERVICE.
To learn more about Supplier Relationships including registrations in the Approved Suppliers Directory click on the following link:
PEMEX – Supplier Relationships


INTERNATIONAL TENDERSAccess the public tendering processes that PPI is conducting or has conducted acting on behalf of Petroleos Mexicanos and its subsidiary entities.
Supplier RatingsPPI considers the use of a rating system that keeps suppliers informed of their performance contributes to establishing a cooperative business relationship.

