Industry News


                Energy            


Tesoro inks transportation and storage deal with Mexico's Pemex




Jul 18, 2017, 7:45pm CDT



Updated Jul 19, 2017, 11:11am CDT






Industries & Tags


                    Energy,                 


            Oil & gas             














Sergio Chapa


Reporter
San Antonio Business Journal













                    Share
                


























