                From left, Pemex Logistics CEO Ignacio Aguilar Alvarez and Tesoro Corp. Executive Vice… more 

                Petroleos Mexicanos            








 



San Antonio-based refining company Tesoro Corp. (NYSE: TSO) has inked a historic transportation and storage deal in Mexico.
Tesoro Executive Vice President Keith Casey flew to Mexico City, where he signed a three-year deal with Pemex Logistics CEO Ignacio Aguilar Alvarez on Tuesday afternoon.













 Enlarge






                            From left, Pemex Logistics CEO Ignacio Aguilar Alvarez and Tesoro Corp. Executive Vice… more 
Petroleos Mexicanos










 


