In This Article






Energy




Oil & gas





























Steve Kean




John Schmitz




Greg Goff




Dean Taylor






 


 















 Enlarge





                Steven J. Kean, president and CEO of Kinder Morgan Inc.            

                Photos by Craig Hartley/HBJ            






